{"tid":372961,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"MMA vs 力威","createTime":"2017-08-24T16:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T23:11:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83f3fdf351f137147490531de17fcd5262840a96","tid":372961,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T16:23:42.000Z","msg":"link 入邊有片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/sports/art/20170824/20131075\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsports%2Fart%2F20170824%2F20131075&d=%2FJ1myWQRjYcggZNcBLABG7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=5041b59b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsports%2Fart%2F20170824%2F20131075&h=913afcfc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/sports/art/20170824/20131075</a><br />\n<br />\n俄MMA選手打死舉重冠軍<br />\n<br />\n3,186<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170824/large/aa0408a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170824%2Flarge%2Faa0408a.gif&h=834938d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■施拉諾夫（箭嘴示）出手過猛把達捷夫打死。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【綜合俄羅斯外電】俄羅斯日前發生一宗令人惋惜的命案，在俄國東南邊疆一城市，一位MMA格鬥選手，因意見不合打死當地一名舉重冠軍，全程更被鏡頭拍攝下來。<br />\n<br />\n根據俄國新聞報道，名叫施拉諾夫（Anar Ziranov）的MMA選手，當時正跟舉重選手達捷夫（Andrey Drachev、小圖）討論打拳與拳擊兩者，那樣運動對身體會更好，怎料二人越辯越激烈，開始有講手迹象，施拉諾就突然一腳踢向達捷夫頸部，後者即時倒地，施拉諾沒有收手，衝上前向已沒甚反應的達捷夫頭部連環出拳，最後要旁人將他拉開。<br />\n<br />\n被施拉諾夫拳打腳踢的達捷夫送院後證實不治，死因是腦部損壞，而施拉諾夫亦即時被逮捕。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n體壇拾趣： 43歲鈴木「最遠」全壘打<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n體訊速遞： （足球）曼聯三傷兵復操"},{"pid":"ff11182c4b2b8e087cbabacae806451982cda7fe","tid":372961,"uid":26942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"力威健埋心的 唔會打架"},{"pid":"d495cafcb307de83a9c083409cbf54f980ea63f1","tid":372961,"uid":48796,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T19:01:47.000Z","msg":"街交出到轉身高踢KO都幾撚勁<br />\n如果對方落地佢唔再打, 應該唔會死<br />\n<br />\nBTW body builder未贏過武術家<br />\n啲人諗住大隻 = 好打係誤解"},{"pid":"a2c15a2c56190e4cbc3fbba85d8ffebca9b03843","tid":372961,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T23:11:54.000Z","msg":"大隻同好打根本冇關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}